title: DDFP 600: Week 3 Red Challenge Flag Picks & Top 3 College QBs
itunes:title: DDFP 600: Week 3 Red Challenge Flag Picks & Top 3 College QBs
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith to discuss the best 2-0 team, the best 1-1 team and best 0-2 team headed into Week 3. Also, the fellas and Cynthia each give their top three rankings of the best quarterbacks in college football. Then, in this edition of "Cynthesize It!" Cynthia breaks down the impact of injury reports on fantasy football and how owners can best navigate those uncertainties. Lastly, EmmaVP reads her Week 3 "TV Guide" descriptions for the biggest matchups of the week for the guys to then preview and pick.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
